title: Cyberpunk Music Pack 1
description: This is a music pack featuring fifteen unique cyberpunk instrumental tracks. Utilizing orchestral and ambient effects, all of these pieces are versatile enough to use across a wide variety of projects.
longDescription:
Music composer, Living Force is proud to present The Cyberpunk Music Pack! This is an asset pack that contains fifteen orchestral/ambient fused instrumentals geared towards the world of Cyberpunk. The pieces all contain a fade-out and are loopable for desired cut scenes, action sequences, and transitions for your projects.
